Ɛmen, yen këcɔl Power series alë bennë lui nï taan bennë kɛk kayïï tɔ nï functionɣic cuɔɔr bikki dir.
Ku nïye kanɣic abï piny liëu bennë ɣaan kɔk thin bï luɔnde (function) nyuɔɔth.
